                  <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph ">As <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>used in this <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 52.244-6 by—
a. Revising the section heading;
