c. Revising paragraph (a);?>clause—</ph>
               </p>
               <p id="d3640e31" class="- topic/p ">
                  <i outputclass="Term" xtrf="_52.244-6" xtrc="d3631e40">Commercial product, commercial service</i> and <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">commercially
available off-the-shelf item</i> have the meanings contained in Federal
Acquisition Regulation (FAR) <xref href="2.101.dita#FAR_2_101"
                        base="FAR_2_101"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>.</p>
